#

Vegan Borscht with Cabbage and Potatoes

45 min
$12
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A hearty and vibrant beet soup packed with vegetables, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 3 medium, peeled and grated
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • carrots: 1 large, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • bay leaf: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • dill: fresh, for garnish
